    public static class ImageIcon.Plain<Rend,Pos,Scalar extends java.lang.Comparable<Scalar>>
extends ImageIcon<Rend,Pos,Scalar,GraphicalPrimitive<Rend,Pos,Scalar>>
    Variant parametrized directly with GraphicalPrimitive instead of any its subtype. A basic DrawableElem implementation that holds a GraphicalPrimitive and renders it on the screen as the representation of itself.

    MarkusSecundus
